&lt;p>In the previous article, we have known the mod and project structure, in this article, we will write some simple code.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="modify-the-mod-information">Modify the Mod Information&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>First, we need delete some useless file.&lt;/p>
