&lt;li>Delete the &lt;code>client&lt;/code> in the &lt;code>gradle.build&lt;/code> file, because we don&amp;rsquo;t need to split the client and server, so we can delete the &lt;code>loom&lt;/code> block in the &lt;code>gradle.build&lt;/code> file.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
